html.content:
Thank you for your information, your download is ready!

Your download should now begin. We hope you enjoy reading our Shell Fleet Solutions newsletters and will continue to provide you with information on all the latest industry trends, tips and tools for managing your fleet.

Ultra-Efficiency or Digital Disruption?

Planning for the Future of Fleets

The commercial fleet sector has long been an industry rooted in tradition. Change, if it happens, has always been incremental. However, a convergence of new technology, services, and greater connectivity will render the sector completely unrecognisable by 2040. This radical reshape will require the development of new skills, industry players, and business models. In the face of such sudden, drastic change, it’s no surprise nearly half of all fleet managers are struggling to stay informed.

We’ve done the legwork for you, compiling the emerging best practices that will guide you in future-proofing your fleet. You will learn:

  • Why the industry is changing, according to experts
  • How the changes will impact you and how to weather them
  • How to be one of the winners in a shifting business landscape

To begin your download, it would be great if you could share some information about you/your business. We’ll use this information to ensure that we better tailor our communications and services to your company’s needs. Thank you for sharing.

DOWNLOAD THE WHITEPAPER

Shell is committed to protecting and respecting your privacy, and we’ll only use your personal information to administer your account and to provide the products and services you requested from us. If you agree we would like to contact you from time to time about our products and services, as well as other content that may be of interest to you. For further information please refer to our B2B Privacy Notice here and our B2C Privacy Notice here, depending on your location.
